title: EPISODE 265: BIG PROBLEMS - Judge Rules for Trump as Weissman Melts Down
description:
It’s “the end of the rule of law”, according to Andrew Weissman as he melted down after Judge Cannon ruled for Donald Trump regarding the Mar-a-Lago documents. President Donald Trump predicted nationwide unrest should he be indicted; Poso analyzes the connection Trump has with his followers as opposed to leftist wine moms who follow career politicians. According to the New York Times propaganda service, the Durham inquiry appears to be winding down as the grand jury expires; Poso holds Sean Hannity accountable and challenges him to join forces to clear out the deep state. FAKE MEAT FAIL: Poso ends on a positive note as he announces that the abhorrent mockery of real food, Beyond Meat’s sales and stock plummeted 74% as the unholy company may go bankrupt.
